[I] Cross-platform Rust rewrite of the GNU coreutils

[T] uutils coreutils is a cross-platform reimplementation of the GNU coreutils
[T] in Rust. While all programs have been implemented, some options might be
[T] missing or different behavior might be experienced.

[U] https://github.com/uutils/coreutils

[A] uutils developers
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/base
[F] CUSTOM-LTO

[L] MIT
[V] 0.7.0

[D] 7a7c28ce0a2939578930359a0b859d5ea733d0078126cfdb6488dffc uutils-coreutils-0.7.0.tar.gz https://github.com/uutils/coreutils/archive/refs/tags/0.7.0/

prefix=opt/$pkg/

var_append cargoinstopt ' ' "--no-default-features -F unix"
[ "$SDECFG_LTO" = 1 ] && export CARGO_PROFILE_RELEASE_LTO=true || export CARGO_PROFILE_RELEASE_LTO=off
